data.description: Check out this charming 3bd 2ba home in the beautiful neighborhood of Meadowlake. The open living area boasts high ceilings and a welcoming gas fireplace. Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, a tile backsplash, and a cozy breakfast nook, leading to a fenced backyard with a covered patio and above-ground pool— great for entertaining. All three bedrooms are spacious, with the master bedroom featuring trey ceilings and a large walk-in closet. The master bathroom offers double sinks, a large jacuzzi tub, and a separate walk-in shower. Recent upgrades include a brand-new HVAC system and hot water heater. The community features a lake that is great for fishing, and the HOA covers front yard maintenance. You don’t want to miss this opportunity, schedule your showing today.
